{"tid":2360533,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蓬佩奧：撤銷對美台官員交流的「自設限制」 指之為「討好中共的單邊措施」","createTime":"2021-01-09T23:10:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-09T23:31:40.000Z","uid":258356,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"34fd87220070e318637db7405cca3ad86161a354","tid":2360533,"uid":258356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T23:10:50.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普政府行將卸任仍繼續挺台。國務卿蓬佩奧周六宣佈，撤銷幾十年來對美國與台灣官員接觸的「自設限制」，勢將觸怒北京。<br />\n<br />\n蓬佩說，為了討好中共，美國國務院「單方面」製造「複雜的內部限制」，管制着美台外交人員、軍事人員等的接觸。他說：「不再了」。<br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n蓬佩奧：撤銷對美台官員交流的「自設限制」 指之為「討好中共的單邊措施」<br />\n <a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210110/HPYKVIEPNJFE3A5OQPSJKVEJC4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210110%2FHPYKVIEPNJFE3A5OQPSJKVEJC4%2F&d=3UqZ%2FPYEUq8PtOmaimGdDRyAur%2Bbp9MVyOkMM5%2FMxDY%3D&h=5e4cbbca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210110%2FHPYKVIEPNJFE3A5OQPSJKVEJC4%2F&h=83d7215a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210110/HPYKVIEPNJFE3A5OQPSJKVEJC4/</a><br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀：<br />\nPompeo lifts US-Taiwan restrictions in move likely to anger China<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/world/2021/jan/09/mike-pompeo-restrictions-us-taiwan-china\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2021%2Fjan%2F09%2Fmike-pompeo-restrictions-us-taiwan-china&d=3UqZ%2FPYEUq8PtOmaimGdDRyAur%2Bbp9MVyOkMM5%2FMxDY%3D&h=4c8cf1fc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.theguardian.com/world/2021/jan/09/mike-pompeo-restrictions-us-taiwan-china</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8e683ade0c02146af1b3b45ed25ee2b68f5415c","tid":2360533,"uid":256837,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T23:16:24.